Software Commons is [a multi-stakeholder cooperative][1] of software producers
and consumers, both corporate and individual. Our purpose is **to sustain a
healthy commons of publicly shared software**. We [balance user freedom and
developer sustainability][2], in order to protect against both [enclosure][3]
and the [tragedy of the commons][4].

