We utilize two mechanisms: [licensing][5]
and [Fair Share][6]. We recognize both [Open Source Projects][7] and [Open
Products][8] as legitimate, and we celebrate sustainable software sharing in
all forms wherever we see it, whether from members of Software Commons or not.

